</section>

<!-- ===== PROCESS PREVIEW ===== -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-reveal>
      <span class="section-eyebrow">How It Works</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">From Design to Handover in 4 Phases</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">A streamlined process that brings certainty to construction. Design, manufacture, assemble, and deliver — all managed by one team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-preview">
      <div class="process-step" data-reveal>
        <span class="process-num">01</span>
        <h3>Design & Engineering</h3>
        <p>Architectural design, structural engineering, and modular optimization. BIM models every module before production.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step" data-reveal>
        <span class="process-num">02</span>
        <h3>Factory Production</h3>
        <p>Modules built in climate-controlled factories with precision tooling. Electrical, plumbing, and finishes installed inline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step" data-reveal>
        <span class="process-num">03</span>
        <h3>Site Assembly</h3>
        <p>Modules transported to site and craned into position. Typical 100-unit building assembled in 2-3 weeks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step" data-reveal>
        <span class="process-num">04</span>
        <h3>Handover</h3>
        <p>Final connections, commissioning, and quality inspection. Keys delivered with full documentation and warranties.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-cta" data-reveal>
      <a href="process.html" class="btn btn-outline">See Full Process →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== SUSTAINABILITY ===== -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="media-split">
      <div class="media-split-img" data-reveal>
        <img src="generated/sustainability-green.webp" alt="Modern modular building with green roof garden and solar panels surrounded by trees" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="media-split-content" data-reveal>
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Sustainability</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Building for a Greener Future</h2>
        <p>Modular construction is inherently sustainable. Factory production reduces material waste to under 3%, compared to 15-20% on traditional sites. Our modules exceed local energy codes by 25%, and our buildings are designed for disassembly — modules can be relocated and reused rather than demolished.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>70% less construction waste sent to landfill</li>
          <li>30% lower embodied carbon per square meter</li>
          <li>Energy-efficient envelopes that exceed code by 25%</li>
          <li>Relocatable design — buildings that can be reused</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="about.html" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

